l Bennet 2020 presidential campaign|Bennet]]\"\n bar:Yang\n  from:11/06/2017 till:02/11/2020 color:DEM text:\"[[Andrew Yang 2020 presidential campaign|Yang]]\"\n bar:Delaney\n  from:07/28/2017 till:01/31/2020 color:DEM text:\"[[John Delaney 2020 presidential campaign|Delaney]]\"\n bar:Booker\n  from:02/01/2019 till:01/13/2020 color:DEM text:\"[[Cory Booker 2020 presidential campaign|Booker]]\"\n bar:Williamson\n  from:11/15/2018 till:01/28/2019 color:Planning\n  from:01/28/2019 till:01/10/2020 color:DEM text:\"[[Marianne Williamson 2020 presidential campaign|Williamson]]\"\n bar:Castro\n  from:12/12/2018 till:01/12/2019 color:Planning\n  from:01/12/2019 till:01/02/2020 color:DEM text:\"[[Julian Castro 2020 presidential campaign|Castro]]\"\n bar:Harris\n  from:01/21/2019 till:12/03/2019 color:DEM text:\"[[Kamala Harris 2020 presidential campaign|Harris]]\"\n bar:Bullock\n  from:05/14/2019 till:12/02/2019 color:DEM text:\"[[Steve Bullock 2020 presidential campaign|Bullock]]\"\n bar:Sestak\n  from:06/22/2019 till:12/01/2019 color:DEM text:\"[[Joe Sestak 2020 presidential campaign|Sestak]]\"\n bar:Messam\n  from:03/13/2019 till:03/28/2019 color:Planning\n  from:03/28/2019 till:11/19/2019 color:DEM text:\"[[Wayne Messam#2020 presidential campaign|Messam]]\"\n bar:O'Rourke \n  from:03/14/2019 till:11/01/2019 color:DEM text:\"[[Beto O'Rourke 2020 presidential campaign|O'Rourke]]\"\n bar:Ryan\n  from:04/04/2019 till:10/24/2019 color:DEM text:\"[[Tim Ryan (Ohio politician)#2020 presidential campaign|Ryan]]\"\n bar:DeBlasio\n  from:05/16/2019 till:09/20/2019 color:DEM text:\"[[Bill de Blasio#2020 presidential campaign|de Blasio]]\"\n bar:Gillibrand\n  from:01/15/2019 till:03/17/2019 color:Planning\n  from:03/17/2019 till:08/28/2019 color:DEM text:\"[[Kirsten Gillibrand 2020 presidential campaign|Gillibrand]]\"\n bar:Moulton\n  from:04/22/2019 till:08/23/2019 color:DEM text:\"[[Seth Moulton#2020 presidential campaign|Moulton]]\"\n bar:Inslee\n  from:03/01/2019 till:08/21/2019 